title: Something about Gujarati food
content:
Hi everyone! I am vedant and I am a gujarati. So, you can trust on the information I give you about gujarati food dishes. "Eating cultural food makes a person more healthy." This statement is proven scientifically in one of the research that shows that the people eating cultural food are usually more proactive and fit than the people who eat more fast food. You can also prove it practically by asking your grandparent or any relative who is 50 years old or more, about the comparision of people who suffered from obesity when they were in their preteens and people suffering from obesity now. The answer you are most likely to get is that the "People suffering from obesity has increased significantly." So what is the solution for it? One of the major solution is eating cultural food. you see obesity rate has been increasing since 1990's which was the era of fast food. The whole world was introduced to fast food at this time. People loved the delicious taste of burgers from mcdonald's, pizzas from domino's and other food items from different restaurants. This made them eat those food items resulting in consumption of lesser cultural food. So, if we start consuming more cultural food again, the results would benefit the whole world including you and your loved ones. Now the problem is, how to find variety of food item so that we can consume different food items at different without repeating them again and again? No problem! this is the correct place you have chosen to know about cultural food. Here are 5 delicious gujarati food items you can eat, that will help you reduce the consumption of fast food. 
1. khandvi
2. ringan nu bhartu
3. sukhdi
4. rotlo
5. dudhi nu shaak
I hope you make your diet more healthy by adding these food items. Obviously, being healthy doesn't only mean to eat healthy food, it also means to do daily excercise like walking, running, yoga, cardio etc. which makes you healthy both physically and mentally.
